{"type":"message","id":"208cbef1","parentId":"a9058375","timestamp":"2026-03-05T17:37:18.221Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_02LWXVAT0h50B7NrcXoHT1p1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n### Step 8 — Update Learning Retrieval Index\n\n**Purpose**:\nMaintain a lightweight retrieval index so the agent can quickly find relevant Pattern‑Keys without scanning full logs.\n\n**Actions**:\n\n1. Read:\n   - `{baseDir}/.learnings/ERRORS.md`\n   - `{baseDir}/.learnings/LEARNINGS.md`\n\n2. Extract all Pattern‑Keys and derive:\n   - domain\n   - tags (3–6)\n   - rule (one line)\n   - promoted_to (AGENTS.md / TOOLS.md / none)\n\n3. Read:\n   - `AGENTS.md`\n   - `TOOLS.md`\n   to detect promoted guardrails.\n\n4. Rebuild `{baseDir}/.learnings/INDEX.md` from scratch with fixed domain sections.\n\n\n[12 more lines in file. Use offset=220 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772732238216}}
