{"type":"message","id":"b44c3493","parentId":"1b148543","timestamp":"2026-03-05T18:55:02.179Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_WvqjxneGAAofdovUWXnmuDQy","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Sub-agent Handoff Report Contract (Option 1)\n\nThis contract must be included in every delegation prompt to sub-agents.\n\n## Required final block (exact format)\nOutcome: success|partial|failure\nIncidents:\n- [TYPE=ERROR|NEAR_MISS|MISUNDERSTANDING|TOOL_FAILURE|MULTI_AGENT_HANDOFF; SEV=S1|S2|S3|S4] <symptom in 1 line> (evidence: <1 line, no secrets>)\nPattern hint: <optional, 1 line>\nPrevention rule: <optional, 1 line>\nFiles touched: <list or \"none\">\nNext action: <1 line>\n\n## Rules\n- Do NOT include secrets/tokens/credentials.\n- Keep evidence brief and concrete.\n- If no incidents: set Incidents: none.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772736902163}}
