{"type":"message","id":"73a22ad5","parentId":"5d1546bd","timestamp":"2026-03-05T18:56:21.694Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now I'll simulate 8 items and produce the plan. I should also mention that each validator will get the handoff report requirement. Let me write the output.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🔧 Guardrail Updates Applied\n\n### 1. **Validator Batch Size Enhanced**\n**Updated in AGENTS.md** with explicit limits and automatic split policy:\n\n```markdown\n- **Hard limit**: 10 minutes (validator timeout window)\n- **Safe budget**: 8 minutes (buffer for reliable completion)\n- **Execution policy**:\n  - If `items_to_validate > 5`, split automatically (no user confirmation).\n  - Prefer batch sizes that keep each validator ≤ safe_budget.\n  - Default split strategy:\n    - 6–9 items: spawn 3 validators (3+3+remaining).\n    - 10–15 items: spawn 3 validators (5+5+remaining) unless time estimate exceeds safe_budget, then use smaller batches.\n```\n\n### 2. **Delegation Template Added**\n**New section in AGENTS.md** with mandatory Handoff Report requirement:\n\n```markdown\n## Delegation Template\nWhen spawning sub‑agents, ALWAYS include the following Handoff Report requirement (non‑optional):\n```\n\n*(Full template included verbatim in AGENTS.md)*\n\n---\n\n## ✅ Self‑Check Simulation: 8 Items\n\n### **Automatic Split Applied**\n**Items to validate**: 8 (exceeds 5‑item limit → automatic split)\n\n**Default strategy for 6–9 items**: spawn 3 validators (3+3+remaining)\n\n**Batch configuration**:\n- Validator A: **3 items** (est. 6 minutes)\n- Validator B: **3 items** (est. 6 minutes)  \n- Validator C: **2 items** (est. 4 minutes)\n\n**Time check**: All batches ≤ safe_budget (8 minutes) ✅\n\n### **Handoff Report Inclusion**\nEach validator will receive the mandatory instruction:\n\n```\n### Mandatory Final Block\nYour final response must end with a structured Handoff Report...\n```\n\n### **Execution Plan (No Confirmation Needed)**\n1. Spawn **Validator A** with 3 items + Handoff Report requirement\n2. Spawn **Validator B** with 3 items + Handoff Report requirement  \n3. Spawn **Validator C** with 2 items + Handoff Report requirement\n4. Aggregate results with Handoff Reports for error‑learning loop\n\n**Total estimated time**: 16 minutes (parallelizable)\n**Risk mitigation**: Each validator runs within 8‑minute safe budget\n\n---\n\n## 🛡️ Guardrail Behavior Verified\n- **Automatic splitting** triggered (8 > 5)\n- **Default strategy** applied (3+3+2)\n- **Time estimates** within safe budget\n- **Handoff Reports** mandatory for all validators\n- **No user confirmation required** per execution policy\n\nThe refined guardrails now prevent timeout incidents while eliminating unnecessary confirmation loops."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":701,"output":658,"cacheRead":66816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68175,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772736957880}}
