{"type":"message","id":"c13ce504","parentId":"82b95514","timestamp":"2026-03-05T19:28:20.769Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Perfecto. La sección \"Delegation Template\" es donde se define lo que debe incluirse al spawnear sub-agents. El usuario quiere agregar: \"Whenever sub-agents are spawned for long-running tasks, automatically register them with the agent-watchdog for monitoring.\" Esto debería agregarse en esa sección, probablemente después de la plantilla del Handoff Report o antes de \"This template must be included...\". \n\nTambién deberíamos definir qué es \"long-running tasks\". Podríamos usar el mismo criterio que en Trigger Heuristics (tasks expected to require multiple reasoning steps >3 steps) o definir un tiempo estimado. Pero el usuario no especifica, así que mantendré simple: \"for long-running tasks (expected runtime >5 minutes)\". \n\nEditaré la sección \"Delegation Template\". Primero leeré el contenido exacto para asegurarme del formato. Ahora haré el edit.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_p0JtvwNbpYPqaV4NW6OCl2VP","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md","oldText":"## Delegation Template\nWhen spawning sub‑agents, ALWAYS include the following Handoff Report requirement (non‑optional):\n\n```\n### Mandatory Final Block\nYour final response must end with a structured Handoff Report using this exact format:\n\n### Handoff Report\n- **Outcome**: success|partial|failure\n- **Incidents**:\n  - [TYPE=ERROR|NEAR_MISS|MISUNDERSTANDING|TOOL_FAILURE|MULTI_AGENT_HANDOFF; SEV=S1|S2|S3|S4] <brief symptom> (evidence: <1‑line concrete detail, no secrets>)\n  - Pattern hint: <optional>\n  - Prevention rule: <optional>\n- **Files touched**: <list or \"none\">\n- **Next action**: <1‑line suggestion>\n\nIf no incidents occurred, write \"Incidents: none\".\nDo NOT include secrets, tokens, or credentials in evidence.\n```\n\nThis template must be included verbatim in all sub‑agent delegation prompts.","newText":"## Delegation Template\nWhen spawning sub‑agents, ALWAYS include the following Handoff Report requirement (non‑optional):\n\n```\n### Mandatory Final Block\nYour final response must end with a structured Handoff Report using this exact format:\n\n### Handoff Report\n- **Outcome**: success|partial|failure\n- **Incidents**:\n  - [TYPE=ERROR|NEAR_MISS|MISUNDERSTANDING|TOOL_FAILURE|MULTI_AGENT_HANDOFF; SEV=S1|S2|S3|S4] <brief symptom> (evidence: <1‑line concrete detail, no secrets>)\n  - Pattern hint: <optional>\n  - Prevention rule: <optional>\n- **Files touched**: <list or \"none\">\n- **Next action**: <1‑line suggestion>\n\nIf no incidents occurred, write \"Incidents: none\".\nDo NOT include secrets, tokens, or credentials in evidence.\n```\n\nThis template must be included verbatim in all sub‑agent delegation prompts.\n\n**Watchdog Registration**: Whenever sub‑agents are spawned for long‑running tasks (expected runtime >5 minutes), automatically register them with the `agent‑watchdog` for stall monitoring and recovery."}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":415,"output":946,"cacheRead":70848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72209,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772738876454}}
