{"type":"message","id":"7736c191","parentId":"af1c9535","timestamp":"2026-03-05T19:41:19.986Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Verificar AGENTS.md existe. Ya sabemos que existe. Confirmar que la arquitectura soporta error-learning-loop, contextual learning retrieval, watchdog monitoring, learning index. Eso parece estar presente.\n\nAhora STEP 2: FIX WATCHDOG REGISTRATION POLICY. Necesito actualizar AGENTS.md en la sección \"## Delegation Template\". Voy a leer esa sección completa para ver el contexto.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ZGvRnp6frypb4UuJ7qmX5pSi","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md","offset":255,"limit":40}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":44621,"output":260,"cacheRead":27584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72465,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772739662820}}
{"type":"message","id":"b75e5394","parentId":"7736c191","timestamp":"2026-03-05T19:41:20.015Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_ZGvRnp6frypb4UuJ7qmX5pSi","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n## Delegation Template\nWhen spawning sub‑agents, ALWAYS include the following Handoff Report requirement (non‑optional):\n\n```\n### Mandatory Final Block\nYour final response must end with a structured Handoff Report using this exact format:\n\n### Handoff Report\n- **Outcome**: success|partial|failure\n- **Incidents**:\n  - [TYPE=ERROR|NEAR_MISS|MISUNDERSTANDING|TOOL_FAILURE|MULTI_AGENT_HANDOFF; SEV=S1|S2|S3|S4] <brief symptom> (evidence: <1‑line concrete detail, no secrets>)\n  - Pattern hint: <optional>\n  - Prevention rule: <optional>\n- **Files touched**: <list or \"none\">\n- **Next action**: <1‑line suggestion>\n\nIf no incidents occurred, write \"Incidents: none\".\nDo NOT include secrets, tokens, or credentials in evidence.\n```\n\nThis template must be included verbatim in all sub‑agent delegation prompts.\n\n**Watchdog Registration**: Whenever sub‑agents are spawned for long‑running tasks (expected runtime >5 minutes), automatically register them with the `agent‑watchdog` for stall monitoring and recovery.\n\n## Make It Yours\n\nThis is a starting point. Add your own conventions, style, and rules as you figure out what works.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772739680002}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a0ccce4","parentId":"b75e5394","timestamp":"2026-03-05T19:41:49.290Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Necesito agregar la subsección \"### Watchdog Registration Procedure\" después del template de Handoff Report. Pero actualmente hay una línea \"**Watchdog Registration**: ...\". Debo reemplazar esa línea con la nueva subsección más detallada. Primero, voy a leer un poco más para ver el formato. Ahora editaré AGENTS.md. Voy a reemplazar desde \"**Watchdog Registration**: ...\" hasta \"## Make It Yours\". Pero mejor reemplazar solo esa línea y agregar el contenido después. Voy a hacerlo en dos pasos: primero reemplazar la línea simple con la subsección completa.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_IFQ4kI11SX8iyAnykV9np2HP","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md","oldText":"**Watchdog Registration**: Whenever sub‑agents are spawned for long‑running tasks (expected runtime >5 minutes), automatically register them with the `agent‑watchdog` for stall monitoring and recovery.","newText":"### Watchdog Registration Procedure\n\nWhenever a sub‑agent is spawned for a long‑running task (expected runtime >5 minutes), the main agent must immediately register the sub‑agent with the `agent‑watchdog`.\n\nThe registration must include the following parameters:\n\n- `session_id`\n- `run_id`\n- `task_description`\n- `expected_runtime`\n- `model`\n- `runtime_type` (`subagent` | `acp`)\n\n**Procedure**:\n\n1. Spawn the sub‑agent.\n2. Capture the returned `session_id` and `run_id`.\n3. Register the sub‑agent with the watchdog.\n4. Start watchdog monitoring.\n5. Allow the watchdog to perform stall recovery if needed.\n\n**Example flow**:\n\n```\nspawn validator_agent_A\nspawn validator_agent_B\n\nregister_watchdog(\n  session_id=\"validator_A_session\",\n  run_id=\"validator_A_run\",\n  task_description=\"validate batch items\",\n  expected_runtime=8,\n  model=\"deepseek‑reasoner\",\n  runtime_type=\"subagent\"\n)\n```\n\nThe watchdog will then:\n\n- Monitor session activity\n- Detect inactivity\n- Perform recovery escalation\n\n**Recovery escalation levels**:\n\n- **Level 1**: send \"continue\"\n- **Level 2**: cancel run and resume task\n- **Level 3**: close session and relaunch agent"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":44684,"output":686,"cacheRead":27840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73210,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772739680016}}
