{"type":"message","id":"4713f105","parentId":"feba7088","timestamp":"2026-03-05T19:42:18.377Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_lQ2Vvt2SOmrehzJhsvSR6EmI","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\ndef recovery_action(attempt):\n    if attempt == 1:\n        return \"nudge_continue\"\n    elif attempt == 2:\n        return \"cancel_and_resume\"\n    elif attempt == 3:\n        return \"relaunch_agent\"\n    else:\n        return \"abort\"\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772739738361}}
{"type":"message","id":"7e3ddf6a","parentId":"4713f105","timestamp":"2026-03-05T19:42:23.371Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Y watchdog_learning_adapter.py:","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_bhdwSqyFJAD0V9kCN7dXFtQL","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-watchdog/scripts/watchdog_learning_adapter.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":167,"output":83,"cacheRead":72256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72506,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772739738377}}
{"type":"message","id":"299d2da0","parentId":"7e3ddf6a","timestamp":"2026-03-05T19:42:23.397Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_bhdwSqyFJAD0V9kCN7dXFtQL","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\ndef generate_incident(model, stall_duration, recovery_level, success):\n    return {\n        \"pattern_key\": f\"model|STALL|{model}|no_response|runtime_stuck\",\n        \"timestamp\": datetime.utcnow().isoformat(),\n        \"stall_duration\": stall_duration,\n        \"recovery_level\": recovery_level,\n        \"success\": success\n    }\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772739743388}}
{"type":"message","id":"99f9d91b","parentId":"299d2da0","timestamp":"2026-03-05T19:42:33.937Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Falta la integración con el sistema de aprendizaje: append incident to ERRORS.md e invocar error-learning-loop. Necesito crear un script principal o extender los existentes. Voy a crear un nuevo script llamado `watchdog_orchestrator.py` que integre monitoreo, recuperación y reporte de incidentes. Pero el usuario dijo \"Do NOT create a new skill.\" ¿Crear un nuevo script dentro de la skill existente está permitido? Probablemente sí, porque es parte de la skill existente. Sin embargo, prefiero modificar los scripts existentes para mantener la simplicidad.\n\nLa mejor opción es actualizar SKILL.md con los pasos operativos y agregar un script de integración. Voy a leer SKILL.md primero.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_slXP7s3UFgq0Dxfm5JBHfxdv","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-watchdog/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":218,"output":388,"cacheRead":72384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72990,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772739743398}}
{"type":"message","id":"2ab12394","parentId":"99f9d91b","timestamp":"2026-03-05T19:42:33.977Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_slXP7s3UFgq0Dxfm5JBHfxdv","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n# agent-watchdog\n\n## Description\nMonitors running agents and detects stalls caused by model hangs or execution deadlocks.\nAttempts automatic recovery and reports operational incidents to the error-learning-loop.\n\n## When to Use\n- Long running tasks\n- Multi-agent workflows\n- Validator batches\n- External tool execution\n\n## When Not to Use\n- Simple conversational tasks\n- Single step responses\n\n## Inputs\n- session_id\n- run_id\n- task_description\n- expected_runtime\n\n## Outputs\n- watchdog_status\n- recovery_actions_taken\n- incident_report\n\n## Instructions\n1. Register the session and run to monitor.\n2. Periodically inspect session state, run state, and last activity timestamp.\n3. If inactivity exceeds stall timeout, classify as stall.\n4. Execute staged recovery:\n   - Level 1: send nudge (\"continue\")\n   - Level 2: cancel run and resume task\n   - Level 3: close session and relaunch agent\n5. Log telemetry about the stall.\n6. Generate structured incident for error-learning-loop.\n\n## Safety Rules\n- Maximum 3 recovery attempts.\n- Never restart agents indefinitely.\n- Always emit incident report.\n\n## Recovery Escalation\nLevel 1: Nudge -> send \"continue\"\nLevel 2: Soft Reset -> cancel run and resume task\nLevel 3: Relaunch -> close session and start new agent\n\n## Learning Loop Integration\nGenerate incidents with pattern key format:\n\nmodel|STALL|<model>|no_response|runtime_stuck\n\nTelemetry fields:\n- model\n- stall_duration\n- recovery_level\n- success_or_failure\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772739753961}}
{"type":"message","id":"6193a1c5","parentId":"2ab12394","timestamp":"2026-03-05T19:43:00.984Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"La skill ya tiene instrucciones, pero falta la implementación concreta de integración. Necesito agregar un paso explícito para append incident a ERRORS.md y invocar error-learning-loop. Voy a actualizar SKILL.md con una nueva sección \"Incident Reporting Procedure\". Pero también necesito actualizar los scripts para que implementen ese flujo.\n\nDado que el tiempo es limitado, voy a actualizar SKILL.md y crear un script de integración que una los componentes. Crearé `watchdog_main.py` que orquesta monitoreo, recuperación y reporte.\n\nPrimero, actualizaré SKILL.md.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_mb2UVrnf00oUEORzegCr9HrI","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-watchdog/SKILL.md","oldText":"## Learning Loop Integration\nGenerate incidents with pattern key format:\n\nmodel|STALL|<model>|no_response|runtime_stuck\n\nTelemetry fields:\n- model\n- stall_duration\n- recovery_level\n- success_or_failure","newText":"## Learning Loop Integration\nGenerate incidents with pattern key format:\n\nmodel|STALL|<model>|no_response|runtime_stuck\n\nTelemetry fields:\n- model\n- stall_duration\n- recovery_level\n- success_or_failure\n\n### Incident Reporting Procedure\nAfter recovery attempts, the watchdog must emit incidents to the learning system:\n\n1. Generate incident telemetry using the schema above.\n2. Append incident to `<workspace>/.learnings/ERRORS.md`.\n3. Invoke the `error-learning-loop` skill to process the incident.\n\n**Incident schema**:\n- pattern_key\n- timestamp\n- model\n- stall_duration\n- recovery_level\n- success\n- task_type\n- items_count\n\n**Integration sequence**:\n- watchdog detects stall\n- → recovery escalation\n- → incident generated\n- → incident appended to ERRORS.md\n- → error-learning-loop executed\n- → deduplication\n- → learning extraction\n- → guardrail promotion\n- → INDEX.md updated"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":43280,"output":620,"cacheRead":29440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73340,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772739753978}}
