{"type":"message","id":"a5b5e9a9","parentId":"9e845615","timestamp":"2026-03-05T19:43:50.890Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ahora insertaré dos nuevas secciones antes de \"## Learning Loop Integration\". Voy a reemplazar desde \"## Learning Loop Integration\" hasta el final con contenido expandido. Pero es más fácil agregar nuevas secciones después de \"## Recovery Escalation\". Voy a hacerlo.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_rfH9x2MTtvwvxTyDFCcsD9tt","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-watchdog/SKILL.md","oldText":"## Recovery Escalation\nLevel 1: Nudge -> send \"continue\"\nLevel 2: Soft Reset -> cancel run and resume task\nLevel 3: Relaunch -> close session and start new agent\n\n## Learning Loop Integration","newText":"## Recovery Escalation\nLevel 1: Nudge -> send \"continue\"\nLevel 2: Soft Reset -> cancel run and resume task\nLevel 3: Relaunch -> close session and start new agent\n\n## ACP Runtime Support\nThe watchdog must monitor both subagent and ACP (Agent Communication Protocol) sessions.\n\n**Parameters**:\n- `runtime_type`: `subagent` | `acp`\n\n**ACP monitoring detects**:\n- ACP process running but no output\n- No session updates\n- Session stalled without completion callback\n\n**ACP stall pattern key**:\n`runtime|STALL|acp_agent|no_response|acp_session_stuck`\n\n## Multi‑Agent Deadlock Detection\nThe watchdog must detect dependency cycles between agents (deadlocks).\n\n**Detection mechanism**:\n1. Track active agents and their dependency relationships.\n   - `agent_id`\n   - `waiting_for_agent_id`\n   - `task_state`\n2. Build a dependency graph of agents.\n3. Periodically check for cycles in the dependency graph.\n\n**Deadlock pattern key**:\n`multi_agent|DEADLOCK|dependency_cycle|agents_waiting`\n\n**Deadlock recovery strategy**:\n- Level 1 — Request progress update from all agents\n- Level 2 — Force resolution of one dependency edge\n- Level 3 — Restart one agent in the cycle\n\n**Deadlock incident telemetry**:\n- pattern_key\n- timestamp\n- cycle_size\n- agents_involved\n- recovery_strategy\n- success\n\n**Reporting**: Deadlock incidents must be appended to `<workspace>/.learnings/ERRORS.md`.\n\n## Learning Loop Integration"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":441,"output":607,"cacheRead":72128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73176,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772739810046}}
