{"type":"message","id":"26d7ae6f","parentId":"fb2c966a","timestamp":"2026-03-05T19:46:48.116Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_TwhwjZhenGjxGq1DLXv3bAfp","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The watchdog will then:\n\n- Monitor session activity\n- Detect inactivity\n- Perform recovery escalation\n\n**Recovery escalation levels**:\n\n- **Level 1**: send \"continue\"\n- **Level 2**: cancel run and resume task\n- **Level 3**: close session and relaunch agent\n\n## Make It Yours\n\nThis is a starting point. Add your own conventions, style, and rules as you figure out what works.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772740008097}}
