mpts one restart.\n\n**Validation Results:**\n- ✅ **Test A (Rate limiting)**: 6 simulated incidents → only 5 appended to ERRORS.md, 6th skipped with console log \"[Watchdog] Rate limit hit for <pattern_key> — skipped append.\"\n- ✅ **Test B (Self‑protection)**: Forced watchdog exception → watchdog‑failure incident appended, INDEX.md updated via fallback rebuild, watchdog restart count = 1 exactly.\n\n**System Status: PRODUCTION‑READY**\n- Rate limiting prevents log explosion while preserving learning signal.\n- Watchdog now self‑monitors and recovers from its own failures.\n- All existing incident pipeline, recovery escalation, and learning‑loop integration remain unchanged.\n\n**Key Decisions:**\n- Use lightweight file‑based cache for rate limiting (no external dependencies).\n- Single restart policy prevents infinite loops while maintaining resilience.\n- Keep changes minimal and surgical — only modified the watchdog orchestrator.\n\n**Next Steps:**\n- Deploy the hardened watchdog + learning system for live agent orchestration.\n- Monitor for real‑world incidents and verify automatic learning extraction and guardrail promotion.\n\n---\n\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":333,"output":869,"cacheRead":36672,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37874,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772745338307}}
