{"type":"message","id":"f0a7dcef","parentId":"b3dfa90c","timestamp":"2026-03-05T21:18:53.703Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Empty. So only SKILL.md created. Let me read SKILL.md to see if it's complete. Let me also check if .taskboards directory exists. Let me create it if not, but maybe the sub-agent will create. Let me wait a bit more. Let me check the sub-agent's progress by looking at the latest messages. Let me use sessions_history with limit 40. But maybe better to wait for completion announcement. The sub-agent might be taking time to write all the scripts. That's okay. I'll wait 5 more minutes. Let me check if any new files appear. Let me do a quick check every minute. Let me write a simple monitoring script but I'll just do exec commands. Let me check if there are any Python files in scripts now. Let me also check if .taskboards directory exists. Let me do that.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_lJlC5A8bYcZriArjZR39HpTU","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace/.taskboards 2>/dev/null || echo \"No .taskboards directory\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":170,"output":422,"cacheRead":50432,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51024,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772745524825}}
