{"type":"message","id":"b1544b46","parentId":"2e7b601f","timestamp":"2026-03-05T21:36:28.187Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Confirmación final: todos los scripts están presentes. Ahora redacto la respuesta final.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🔥 Fire‑Test Complete: Skill Created & Operational\n\n### 📦 **Sub‑agent Handoff Report**\n\n**Outcome**: `success`  \n**Incidents**: none  \n**Files created** (full structure in `skills/long‑prompt‑orchestrator/`):\n\n- **Documentation**: `SKILL.md` (complete step‑by‑step), `references/design.md`, `references/pattern_keys.md`\n- **Examples**: `example_basic.md`, `example_complex.md` (ready‑to‑run scenarios)\n- **Scripts** (all Python, production‑ready):\n  - `orchestrate.py` – main orchestrator with demo modes\n  - `decompose.py` – detection & prompt splitting\n  - `todo.py` – persistent checklist with 3‑state tracking\n  - `token_budget.py` – global/per‑step token limits\n  - `validate.py` – final‑output validation\n  - `recovery.py` – resume from interruptions\n  - `learning_emit.py` – incident emission to `.learnings/`\n- **Workspace directories**: `.taskboards/` & `.taskboards/checkpoints/` (auto‑created)\n\n---\n\n### ✅ **Main Agent Acceptance Check**\n\n| Component | Result | Evidence |\n|-----------|--------|----------|\n| **Folder exists** | ✅ PASS | `skills/long‑prompt‑orchestrator/` created with all required subdirectories |\n| **Demo runs** | ✅ PASS | `python3 orchestrate.py --demo basic` & `--demo complex` execute fully |\n| **.taskboards files created** | ✅ PASS | Checklists (`demo_basic_*.md`, `demo_complex_*.md`) and checkpoints written |\n| **Incidents → ERRORS.md** | ✅ PASS | 3 incidents emitted (recovery failure, validation failure, token budget) |\n| **INDEX.md refreshed** | ✅ PASS | Timestamp updated from `15:11:28` → `16:33:24` (fallback rebuild triggered) |\n| **Decomposition** | ✅ PASS | Heuristics detect long/complex prompts;