{"type":"message","id":"4f5895e2","parentId":"91ef77e2","timestamp":"2026-03-05T21:52:17.309Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Los permisos son normales.\n\nTal vez el archivo SKILL.md necesita tener extensión .md exactamente. Sí.\n\nPodríamos intentar renombrar el skill a \"watchdog\" solo para probar. Pero mejor no.\n\nOtra posibilidad: el gateway necesita reiniciarse porque cachea la lista de skills al inicio. Como el skill existía antes pero sin frontmatter, quizás fue indexado como no válido y cacheado. Necesitamos reiniciar el gateway. Podemos hacerlo con `openclaw gateway restart`. Pero eso podría interrumpir la sesión actual. Sin embargo, estamos en webchat, que probablemente se conecta al gateway. Si reiniciamos el gateway, la conexión podría perderse, pero el CLI debería seguir funcionando.\n\nPodemos intentar reiniciar el gateway. Primero, verifiquemos el estado del gateway.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_HSXgoVRx0TFd7rsh2lYl4INX","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway status 2>&1 | head -20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":544,"output":441,"cacheRead":74240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75225,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772747528110}}
{"type":"message","id":"c72f08ad","parentId":"4f5895e2","timestamp":"2026-03-05T21:52:19.651Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_HSXgoVRx0TFd7rsh2lYl4INX","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Service: systemd (enabled)\nFile logs: /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-03-05.log\nCommand: /usr/bin/node /home/openclaw/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/entry.js gateway --port 18789\nService file: ~/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-gateway.service\nService env: OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT=18789\n\nConfig (cli): ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\nConfig (service): ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n\nGateway: bind=loopback (127.0.0.1), port=18789 (service args)\nProbe target: ws://127.0.0.1:18789\nDashboard: http://127.0.0.1:18789/\nProbe note: Loopback-only gateway; only local clients can connect.\n\nRuntime: running (pid 23341, state active, sub running, last exit 0, reason 0)\nRPC probe: ok\n\nListening: 127.0.0.1:18789\nTroubles: run openclaw status\nTroubleshooting: https://docs.openclaw.ai/troubleshooting"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2324,"aggregated":"Service: systemd (enabled)\nFile logs: /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-03-05.log\nCommand: /usr/bin/node /home/openclaw/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/entry.js gateway --port 18789\nService file: ~/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-gateway.service\nService env: OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT=18789\n\nConfig (cli): ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\nConfig (service): ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n\nGateway: bind=loopback (127.0.0.1), port=18789 (service args)\nProbe target: ws://127.0.0.1:18789\nDashboard: http://127.0.0.1:18789/\nProbe note: Loopback-only gateway; only local clients can connect.\n\nRuntime: running (pid 23341, state active, sub running, last exit 0, reason 0)\nRPC probe: ok\n\nListening: 127.0.0.1:18789\nTroubles: run openclaw status\nTroubleshooting: https://docs.openclaw.ai/troubleshooting","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772747539640