{"type":"message","id":"0bb32ab0","parentId":"870c1cbc","timestamp":"2026-03-05T22:03:14.615Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"¡Interesante! El skill `test-watchdog` aparece inmediatamente. Entonces el sistema de descubrimiento funciona. Pero `agent-watchdog` no aparece. La diferencia podría ser en los requisitos (`requires`). `test-watchdog` solo requiere `workspace_write`, mientras que `agent-watchdog` requiere `[\"workspace_write\",\"python\"]`. ¿Será que `python` no está disponible como requirement? Pero `long-prompt-orchestrator` también requiere `python` y aparece. Revisemos sus requisitos:","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_wOyRBqgp4mHXclaV2fSFFH6E","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/long-prompt-orchestrator/SKILL.md","offset":1,"limit":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":183,"output":333,"cacheRead":78464,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78980,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772748186676}}
{"type":"message","id":"25539954","parentId":"0bb32ab0","timestamp":"2026-03-05T22:03:14.687Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_wOyRBqgp4mHXclaV2fSFFH6E","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: long-prompt-orchestrator\ndescription: A production-ready Long Prompt Optimizer that automatically decomposes overly long/complex tasks into smaller dependent mini-prompts executed sequentially, manages token budgets, maintains persistent ToDo checklists, validates final output, and supports recovery from interruptions.\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\":{\"category\":\"planning\",\"user-invocable\":true,\"command-dispatch\":\"model\",\"requires\":[\"python\",\"workspace_write\"],\"optional_requires\":[\"bash\"],\"safety_level\":\"high\",\"wrap_up_enabled\":false}}\n---\n\n# long-prompt-orchestrator\n\n## Purpose\nAutomatically detect overly long prompts or complex tasks, decompose them into smaller dependent mini-prompts, execute them sequentially, maintain a persistent ToDo checklist with state tracking, manage token budgets per API call, optimize context to reduce hallucinations, validate final output against original objective, and support recovery from interruptions.\n\n[189 more lines in file. Use offset=11 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772748194672}}
{"type":"message","id":"2c69111e","parentId":"25539954","timestamp":"2026-03-05T22:03:30.694Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"`long-prompt-orchestrator` requiere `[\"python\",\"workspace_write\"]` (en orden diferente). `agent-watchdog` requiere `[\"workspace_write\",\"python\"]`. Eso no debería importar.\n\nProbemos modificar `agent-watchdog/SKILL.md` para que tenga exactamente los mismos requisitos que `long-prompt-orchestrator`. Pero antes, verifiquemos si hay algún error en el archivo SKILL.md de `agent-watchdog`. Podría haber un problema de encoding o un carácter invisible.\n\nTambién podríamos eliminar el skill y recrearlo. Pero primero, hagamos una copia de seguridad y creemos una versión simplificada. Modifiquemos el frontmatter para que sea idéntico al de `long-prompt-orchestrator` pero con name y descripción diferentes.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_WD8UFizvD9Sayzp7vKBkCAXm","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-watchdog/SKILL.md","oldText":"---\nname: agent-watchdog\ndescription: Monitors running agents and detects stalls caused by model hangs or execution deadlocks. Attempts automatic recovery and reports operational incidents to the error-learning-loop.\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\":{\"category\":\"meta\",\"user-invocable\":true,\"command-dispatch\":\"model\",\"requires\":[\"workspace_write\",\"python\"],\"optional_requires\":[\"sessions_list\",\"sessions_history\"],\"safety_level\":\"high\",\"wrap_up_enabled\":false}}\n---","newText":"---\nname: agent-watchdog\ndescription: Monitors running agents and detects stalls caused by model hangs or execution deadlocks. Attempts automatic recovery and reports operational incidents to the error-learning-loop.\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\":{\"category\":\"meta\",\"user-invocable\":true,\"command-dispatch\":\"model\",\"requires\":[\"python\",\"workspace_write\"],\"optional_requires\":[\"sessions_list\",\"sess