{"type":"message","id":"284ebdd7","parentId":"9101e922","timestamp":"2026-03-05T22:11:57.471Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_ZOOUBGGPau2OP4t4Up1e0Fhg","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n---\nname: agent-watchdog\ndescription: Monitors running agents and detects stalls caused by model hangs or execution deadlocks. Attempts automatic recovery and reports operational incidents to the error-learning-loop.\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\":{\"category\":\"meta\",\"user-invocable\":true,\"command-dispatch\":\"model\",\"requires\":[\"workspace_write\"],\"optional_requires\":[\"python\",\"sessions_list\",\"sessions_history\"],\"safety_level\":\"high\",\"wrap_up_enabled\":false}}\n---\n\n# agent-watchdog\n\n## Description\nMonitors running agents and detects stalls caused by model hangs or execution deadlocks.\nAttempts automatic recovery and reports operational incidents to the error-learning-loop.\n\n## When to Use\n- Long running tasks\n- Multi-agent workflows\n- Validator batches\n- External tool execution\n\n## When Not to Use\n- Simple conversational tasks\n- Single step responses\n\n## Inputs\n- session_id\n- run_id\n- task_description\n- expected_runtime\n\n## Outputs\n\n[107 more lines in file. Use offset=31 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772748717456}}
