{"type":"message","id":"fbfc7f87","parentId":"3169fc59","timestamp":"2026-03-05T22:23:52.659Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ahora tenemos un skill `agent-watchdog` reconstruido con el SKILL.md corregido y todos los scripts y referencias. Ahora necesitamos reiniciar el gateway para que detecte el skill. Primero, vamos a verificar que el archivo SKILL.md se vea bien. Vamos a leer las primeras líneas.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_D6MZDO8UuxclNlGngHtAnnuL","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-watchdog/SKILL.md","offset":1,"limit":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":208,"output":246,"cacheRead":83712,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84166,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772749426038}}
{"type":"message","id":"8a57e007","parentId":"fbfc7f87","timestamp":"2026-03-05T22:23:52.745Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_D6MZDO8UuxclNlGngHtAnnuL","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: agent-watchdog\ndescription: Monitors running agents and detects stalls caused by model hangs or execution deadlocks. Attempts automatic recovery and reports operational incidents to the error-learning-loop.\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\":{\"category\":\"meta\",\"user-invocable\":true,\"command-dispatch\":\"model\",\"requires\":[\"workspace_write\"],\"optional_requires\":[\"sessions_history\",\"python\",\"bash\"],\"safety_level\":\"high\",\"wrap_up_enabled\":true}}\n---\n\n# agent-watchdog\n\n## Description\nMonitors running agents and detects stalls caused by model hangs or execution deadlocks.\nAttempts automatic recovery and reports operational incidents to the error-learning-loop.\n\n## When to Use\n- Long running tasks\n- Multi-agent workflows\n\n[120 more lines in file. Use offset=16 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772749432703}}
