Supports manual invocation and end-  │                    │\\n│           │                  │ of-task wrap-up.                                                │                    │\\n│ ✓ ready   │ 📦 long-prompt-   │ A production-ready Long Prompt Optimizer that automatically     │ openclaw-workspace │\\n│           │ orchestrator     │ decomposes overly long/complex tasks into smaller dependent     │                    │\\n│           │                  │ mini-prompts executed sequentially, manages token budgets,      │                    │\\n│           │                  │ maintains persistent ToDo checklists, validates final output,   │                    │\\n│           │                  │ and supports recovery from interruptions.                       │                    │\\n│ ✓ ready   │ 📦 test-skill-123 │ Test skill.                                                     │ openclaw-workspace │\\n│ ✓ ready   │ 📦 watchdog-test  │ Test watchdog.                                                  │ openclaw-workspace │\\n└───────────┴──────────────────┴─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┴────────────────────┘\\n\\nTip: use `npx clawhub` to search, install, and sync skills.\",\"_meta\":{\"runtime\":\"node\",\"runtimeVersion\":\"22.22.0\",\"hostname\":\"unknown\",\"name\":\"openclaw\",\"date\":\"2026-03-05T22:21:34.152Z\",\"logLevelId\":3,\"logLevelName\":\"INFO\",\"path\":{\"fullFilePath\":\"file:///home/openclaw/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-kl-vrkYi.js:258:46\",\"fileName\":\"subsystem-kl-vrkYi.js\",\"fileNameWithLine\":\"subsystem-kl-vrkYi.js:258\",\"fileColumn\":\"46\",\"fileLine\":\"258\",\"filePath\":\"/home/openclaw/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-kl-vrkYi.js\",\"filePathWithLine\":\"/home/openclaw/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-kl-vrkYi.js:258\",\"method\":\"console.log\"}},\"time\":\"2026-03-05T17:21:34.154-05:00\"}\n{\"0\":\"{\\\"subsystem\\\":\\\"gateway/ws\\\"}\",\"1\":\"⇄ res ✓ skills.status 222ms conn=7283b484…f323 id=7ef0cc80…3459\",\"_meta\":{\"runtime\":\"node\",\"runtimeVersion\":\"22.22.0\",\"hostname\":\"unknown\",\"name\":\"{\\\"subsystem\\\":\\\"gateway/ws\\\"}\",\"parentNames\":[\"openclaw\"],\"date\":\"2026-03-05T22:23:14.621Z\",\"logLevelId\":3,\"logLevelName\":\"INFO\",\"path\":{\"fullFilePath\":\"file:///home/openclaw/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-BfkFJ4uQ.js:427:14\",\"fileName\":\"subsystem-BfkFJ4uQ.js\",\"fileNameWithLine\":\"subsystem-BfkFJ4uQ.js:427\",\"fileColumn\":\"14\",\"fileLine\":\"427\",\"filePath\":\".npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-BfkFJ4uQ.js\",\"filePathWithLine\":\".npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-BfkFJ4uQ.js:427\",\"method\":\"logToFile\"}},\"time\":\"2026-03-05T17:23:14.621-05:00\"}","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772749513614}}
{"type":"message","id":"75b16c8b","parentId":"ae42cbae","timestamp":"2026-03-05T22:25:30.547Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesante! Veo en los logs que `agent-watchdog` SÍ está siendo detectado como skill:\n\n```\n[info] [gateway] skill agent-watchdog loaded from /home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-watchdog/SKILL.md\n```\n\nEntonces el gateway SÍ está cargando el skill. Pero cuando ejecuto `openclaw skills list` desde la línea de comandos, no aparece. Esto sugiere que hay una desconexión entre el gateway (que corre como servicio) y el comando CLI `openclaw skills list`.\n\nPosibles explicaciones:\n1. El comando CLI consulta una caché diferente\n2. Hay un problema de comunicación entre el CLI y el gateway\n3. El CLI está filtrando skills basado en algún criterio\n\nVoy a verificar si el gateway está realmente corriendo y si el CLI se está comunicando correctamente con él. También puedo intentar usar `curl` para consultar directamente el API del gateway (si tiene uno).\n\nPrimero, verificaré el estado del gateway y si hay algún problema de conexión. Luego puedo intentar forzar una recarga de skills enviando un mensaje al gateway. Ya intenté `openclaw agent --message \"refresh skills\"` pero no estoy seguro de que funcione.\n\nOtra idea: tal vez el comando `openclaw skills list` solo muestra skills que son \"user-invocable\" (invocables por el usuario) o que tienen cierta categoría. En el frontmatter de `agent-watchdog` dice `\"user-invocable\":true`, así que eso debería estar bien.\n\nVoy a examinar el frontmatter de `error-learning-loop` que SÍ aparece en la lista, para comparar. También puedo ver el de `long-prompt-orchestrator` que también aparece. Primero obtengo los frontmatter de estos skills para comparar.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_i2jHCwatx4DQUD2V9fCmrCRW","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/error-learning-loop/SKILL.md","offset":1,"limit":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":9900,"output":941,"cacheRead":65152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75993,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772749513638}}
{"type":"message","id":"5a09adbd","parentId":"75b16c8b","timestamp":"2026-03-05T22:25:30.593Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_i2jHCwatx4DQUD2V9fCmrCRW","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: error-learning-loop\ndescription: Capture errors and near-misses from the current task and from sub-agent handoff reports, perform semantic deduplication of incidents, convert them into actionable learnings, and promote guardrails into AGENTS.md and TOOLS.md so the main agent avoids repeating mistakes. Supports manual invocation and end-of-task wrap-up.\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\":{\"category\":\"meta\",\"user-invocable\":true,\"command-dispatch\":\"model\",\"requires\":[\"workspace_write\"],\"optional_requires\":[\"sessions_history\",\"python\",\"bash\"],\"safety_level\":\"high\",\"wrap_up_enabled\":true}}\n---\n\n# error-learning-loop\n\n## Purpose\nCreate a structured feedback loop where the **main agent** learns from:\n\n[221 more lines in file. Use offset=11 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772749530567}}
