er data, severe      │                    │\\n│           │                  │ weather alerts, or detailed meteorological analysis. No API     │                    │\\n│           │                  │ key needed.                                                     │                    │\\n│ ✗ missing │ 𝕏 xurl           │ A CLI tool for making authenticated requests to the X           │ openclaw-bundled   │\\n│           │                  │ (Twitter) API. Use this skill when you need to post tweets,     │                    │\\n│           │                  │ reply, quote, search, read posts, manage followers, send DMs,   │                    │\\n│           │                  │ upload media, or interact with any X API v2 endpoint.           │                    │\\n│ ✓ ready   │ 📦 agent-watchdog │ Monitors running agents and detects stalls caused by model      │ openclaw-workspace │\\n│           │                  │ hangs or execution deadlocks.                                   │                    │\\n│ ✓ ready   │ 📦 error-         │ Capture errors and near-misses from the current task and from   │ openclaw-workspace │\\n│           │ learning-loop    │ sub-agent handoff reports, perform semantic deduplication of    │                    │\\n│           │                  │ incidents, convert them into actionable learnings, and promote  │                    │\\n│           │                  │ guardrails into AGENTS.md and TOOLS.md so the main agent        │                    │\\n│           │                  │ avoids repeating mistakes. Supports manual invocation and end-  │                    │\\n│           │                  │ of-task wrap-up.                                                │                    │\\n│ ✓ ready   │ 📦 long-prompt-   │ A production-ready Long Prompt Optimizer that automatically     │ openclaw-workspace │\\n│           │ orchestrator     │ decomposes overly long/complex tasks into smaller dependent     │                    │\\n│           │                  │ mini-prompts executed sequentially, manages token budgets,      │                    │\\n│           │                  │ maintains persistent ToDo checklists, validates final output,   │                    │\\n│           │                  │ and supports recovery from interruptions.                       │                    │\\n└───────────┴──────────────────┴─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┴────────────────────┘\\n\\nTip: use `npx clawhub` to search, install, and sync skills.\",\"_meta\":{\"runtime\":\"node\",\"runtimeVersion\":\"22.22.0\",\"hostname\":\"unknown\",\"name\":\"openclaw\",\"date\":\"2026-03-05T22:14:37.162Z\",\"logLevelId\":3,\"logLevelName\":\"INFO\",\"path\":{\"fullFilePath\":\"file:///home/openclaw/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-kl-vrkYi.js:258:46\",\"fileName\":\"subsystem-kl-vrkYi.js\",\"fileNameWithLine\":\"subsystem-kl-vrkYi.js:258\",\"fileColumn\":\"46\",\"fileLine\":\"258\",\"filePath\":\"/home/openclaw/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-kl-vrkYi.js\",\"filePathWithLine\":\"/home/openclaw/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-kl-vrkYi.js:258\",\"method\":\"console.log\"}},\"time\":\"2026-03-05T17:14:37.165-05:00\"}\n{\"0\":\"Skill \\\"agent-watchdog\\\" not found. Run `openclaw skills list` to see available skills.\\n\\nTip: use `npx clawhub` to search, install, and sync skills.\",\"_meta\":{\"runtime\":\"node\",\"runtimeVersion\":\"22.22.0\",\"hostname\":\"unknown\",\"name\":\"openclaw\",\"date\":\"2026-03-05T22:15:41.571Z\",\"logLevelId\":3,\"logLevelName\":\"INFO\",\"path\":{\"fullFilePath\":\"file:///home/openclaw/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-kl-vrkYi.js:258:46\",\"fileName\":\"subsystem-kl-vrkYi.js\",\"fileNameWithLine\":\"subsystem-kl-vrkYi.js:258\",\"fileColumn\":\"46\",\"fileLine\":\"258\",\"filePath\":\"/home/openclaw/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-kl-vrkYi.js\",\"file