TS.md and TOOLS.md so the main agent        │                    │\\n│           │                  │ avoids repeating mistakes. Supports manual invocation and end-  │                    │\\n│           │                  │ of-task wrap-up.                                                │                    │\\n│ ✓ ready   │ 📦 long-prompt-   │ A production-ready Long Prompt Optimizer that automatically     │ openclaw-workspace │\\n│           │ orchestrator     │ decomposes overly long/complex tasks into smaller dependent     │                    │\\n│           │                  │ mini-prompts executed sequentially, manages token budgets,      │                    │\\n│           │                  │ maintains persistent ToDo checklists, validates final output,   │                    │\\n│           │                  │ and supports recovery from interruptions.                       │                    │\\n│ ✓ ready   │ 📦 watchdog-      │ Minimal test.                                                   │ openclaw-workspace │\\n│           │ minimal          │                                                                 │                    │\\n└───────────┴──────────────────┴─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┴────────────────────┘\\n\\nTip: use `npx clawhub` to search, install, and sync skills.\",\"_meta\":{\"runtime\":\"node\",\"runtimeVersion\":\"22.22.0\",\"hostname\":\"unknown\",\"name\":\"openclaw\",\"date\":\"2026-03-05T22:20:53.251Z\",\"logLevelId\":3,\"logLevelName\":\"INFO\",\"path\":{\"fullFilePath\":\"file:///home/openclaw/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-kl-vrkYi.js:258:46\",\"fileName\":\"subsystem-kl-vrkYi.js\",\"fileNameWithLine\":\"subsystem-kl-vrkYi.js:258\",\"fileColumn\":\"46\",\"fileLine\":\"258\",\"filePath\":\"/home/openclaw/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-kl-vrkYi.js\",\"filePathWithLine\":\"/home/openclaw/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-kl-vrkYi.