{"type":"message","id":"a465c98f","parentId":"983a8a0a","timestamp":"2026-03-05T22:32:25.388Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_MKlWpgc5N1ooRfyAwhZYTDw9","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nsummary: \"CLI reference for `openclaw skills` (list/info/check) and skill eligibility\"\nread_when:\n  - You want to see which skills are available and ready to run\n  - You want to debug missing binaries/env/config for skills\ntitle: \"skills\"\n---\n\n# `openclaw skills`\n\nInspect skills (bundled + workspace + managed overrides) and see what’s eligible vs missing requirements.\n\nRelated:\n\n- Skills system: [Skills](/tools/skills)\n- Skills config: [Skills config](/tools/skills-config)\n- ClawHub installs: [ClawHub](/tools/clawhub)\n\n## Commands\n\n```bash\nopenclaw skills list\nopenclaw skills list --eligible\nopenclaw skills info <name>\nopenclaw skills check\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772749945375}}
