{"type":"message","id":"d84be4c7","parentId":"5440f0ee","timestamp":"2026-03-05T23:25:41.208Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ahora actualizaré stage1_discovery.py para agregar la verificación de EC0249 y modificar el reporte. Primero, buscaré la función run_discovery y agregaré la validación al inicio. También necesito modificar la generación del reporte para incluir el encabezado EC0249.\n\nVoy a leer más del archivo stage1_discovery.py para entender su estructura.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_NtTT0KtqeyqHeGYex6ovHd9N","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/salesforce-architect/scripts/stage1_discovery.py","offset":30,"limit":100}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":1458,"output":273,"cacheRead":97280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99011,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772753131946}}
{"type":"message","id":"90634103","parentId":"d84be4c7","timestamp":"2026-03-05T23:25:41.238Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_NtTT0KtqeyqHeGYex6ovHd9N","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        line_lower = line.lower()\n        # Actors: mentions of roles\n        if any(role in line_lower for role in ['agent', 'manager', 'director', 'advisor', 'staff', 'user', 'customer', 'client']):\n            actors.append(line.strip())\n        # Processes: verbs\n        if any(verb in line_lower for verb in ['track', 'manage', 'handle', 'create', 'send', 'assign', 'route', 'escalate']):\n            processes.append(line.strip())\n        # Events: words like 'when', 'if', 'trigger'\n        if any(word in line_lower for word in ['when', 'if', 'trigger', 'after', 'before']):\n            events.append(line.strip())\n        # Systems: known system names\n        if any(sys in line_lower for sys in ['salesforce', 'cloud', 'erp', 'crm', 'portal', 'chatbot', 'email', 'phone']):\n            systems.append(line.strip())\n        # Unknowns: question marks\n        if '?' in line:\n            unknowns.append(line.strip())\n    \n    # Deduplicate\n    actors = list(set(actors))[:10]\n    processes = list(set(processes))[:10]\n    events = list(set(events))[:10]\n    systems = list(set(systems))[:10]\n    unknowns = list(set(unknowns))[:10]\n    \n    return actors, processes, events, systems, unknowns\n\ndef generate_discovery_report(project, actors, processes, events, systems, unknowns):\n    \"\"\"Generate Discovery_Report.md.\"\"\"\n    content = f\"\"\"# Discovery Report\n\n## Project: {project['project_name']}\n\n### Executive Summary\nThis document summarizes the discovery findings for the {project['project_name']} project.\n\n### Identified Elements\n\n#### Actors\n{chr(10).join(f'- {a}' for a in actors)}\n\n#### Processes\n{chr(10).join(f'- {p}' for p in processes)}\n\n#### Events\n{chr(10).join(f'- {e}' for e in events)}\n\n#### Systems\n{chr(10).join(f'- {s}' for s in systems)}\n\n#### Unknowns & Risks\n{chr(10).join(f'- {u}' for u in unknowns)}\n\n### Recommendations\n- Clarify unknowns with client.\n- Validate processes against Salesforce capabilities.\n- Confirm licensing for identified systems.\n\"\"\"\n    return content\n\ndef generate_process_analysis(processes):\n    \"\"\"Generate Discovery_Process_Analysis.md.\"\"\"\n    content = \"\"\"# Discovery Process Analysis\n\n## Process Narratives\n\n\"\"\"\n    for i, proc in enumerate(processes, 1):\n        content += f\"\"\"### Process {i}: {proc}\n\n**Description**: (to be filled from detailed analysis)\n\n**Steps**:\n1. Step 1\n2. Step 2\n\n**Systems Involved**: \n- Salesforce\n\n**Actors**: \n- Actor\n\n**Dependencies**: \n- None identified\n\n\"\"\"\n    return content\n\ndef generate_discovery_qa(actors, processes, events, systems, unknowns):\n    \"\"\"Generate Discovery_QA.xlsx with tabs.\"\"\"\n    with pd.ExcelWriter('Discovery_QA.xlsx', engine='openpyxl') as writer:\n        # Actors\n        df_actors = pd.DataFrame(actors, columns=['Role'])\n        df_actors['Profile'] = ''\n        df_actors['License'] = ''\n        df_actors['Count'] = ''\n        df_actors.to_excel(writer, sheet_name='Actors', index=False)\n        \n        # Processes\n        df_processes = pd.DataFrame(processes, columns=['Name'])\n        df_processes['Description'] = ''\n\n[69 more lines in file. Use offset=130 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772753141218}}
{"type":"message","id":"71a16c03","parentId":"90634103","timestamp":"2026-03-05T23:25:51.487Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Veo que hay una función `run_discovery` que toma `project_dir` y `inputs`. Agregaré una función `_check_ec0249_reference` que busque el PDF y devuelva la ruta o None. Luego, al inicio de `run_discovery`, llamaré a esa función. Si no encuentra el PDF, emitirá un incidente usando learning_emit.py (que debe estar importado) y generará un Discovery_Report.md con el mensaje de bloqueo.\n\nTambién necesito modificar la generación del reporte para incluir el encabezado \"Discovery executed under EC0249 methodology\". Buscaré dónde se escribe Discovery_Report.md.\n\nVeo que hay una función `generate_discovery_report`. Necesito ver su contenido.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_62SqwB9c9WPizn0uY52HkUaT","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/salesforce-architect/scripts/stage1_discovery.py","offset":130,"limit":80}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":263,"output":435,"cacheRead":98688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99386,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772753141238}}
{"type":"message","id":"8cd52a35","parentId":"71a16c03","timestamp":"2026-03-05T23:25:51.524Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_62SqwB9c9WPizn0uY52HkUaT","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        df_processes['Trigger'] = ''\n        df_processes['Outcome'] = ''\n        df_processes['Complexity'] = ''\n        df_processes.to_excel(writer, sheet_name='Processes', index=False)\n        \n        # Events\n        df_events = pd.DataFrame(events, columns=['Name'])\n        df_events['Trigger'] = ''\n        df_events['Process'] = ''\n        df_events['System'] = ''\n        df_events.to_excel(writer, sheet_name='Events', index=False)\n        \n        # Systems\n        df_systems = pd.DataFrame(systems, columns=['Name'])\n        df_systems['Type'] = ''\n        df_systems['Integration Required'] = ''\n        df_systems['Notes'] = ''\n        df_systems.to_excel(writer, sheet_name='Systems', index=False)\n        \n        # Unknowns\n        df_unknowns = pd.DataFrame(unknowns, columns=['Question'])\n        df_unknowns['Impact'] = ''\n        df_unknowns['Priority'] = ''\n        df_unknowns['Assigned To'] = ''\n        df_unknowns.to_excel(writer, sheet_name='Unknowns', index=False)\n\ndef run_stage1(project_root, inputs):\n    \"\"\"\n    Execute Stage 1.\n    \"\"\"\n    logger.info('Running Stage 1: Discovery')\n    \n    # Extract from transcript if provided\n    text = ''\n    if 'discovery_transcript' in inputs:\n        text = inputs['discovery_transcript']\n    else:\n        text = inputs.get('process_description', '')\n    \n    actors, processes, events, systems, unknowns = extract_ec0249(text)\n    \n    # Generate outputs\n    report = generate_discovery_report(inputs, actors, processes, events, systems, unknowns)\n    analysis = generate_process_analysis(processes)\n    \n    report_path = project_root / 'discovery' / 'Discovery_Report.md'\n    analysis_path = project_root / 'discovery' / 'Discovery_Process_Analysis.md'\n    qa_path = project_root / 'discovery' / 'Discovery_QA.xlsx'\n    \n    ensure_dir(project_root / 'discovery')\n    report_path.write_text(report, encoding='utf-8')\n    analysis_path.write_text(analysis, encoding='utf-8')\n    \n    # Generate Excel\n    generate_discovery_qa(actors, processes, events, systems, unknowns)\n    # Move file\n    import shutil\n    shutil.move('Discovery_QA.xlsx', qa_path)\n    \n    logger.info('Stage 1 completed. Outputs saved to %s', project_root / 'discovery')\n    return True\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    # Test with dummy inputs\n    test_inputs = {\n        'project_name': 'Test',\n        'discovery_transcript': 'We need agents to manage cases. When a customer calls, assign to agent. Use Salesforce Cloud.'\n    }\n    run_stage1(Path('.'), test_inputs)"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772753151507}}
