{"type":"message","id":"acdd15eb","parentId":"e06132fc","timestamp":"2026-03-05T23:29:43.687Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_isItQ3yzm41UdX6PsQ895Q6S","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n### Stage 0 – Intake Gate\n**Mandatory inputs** (block pipeline if missing):\n- Project name\n- Industry\n- Country\n- Salesforce clouds licensed\n- User count\n- Process description\n- Implementation scope\n\nIf any mandatory input is missing, generate discovery questions and stop.\n\n### Stage 1 – Discovery (EC0249)\nExtract actors, processes, events, systems, unknowns from transcripts/notes/SOW.\n**Outputs:**\n- `Discovery_Report.md`\n- `Discovery_Process_Analysis.md`\n- `Discovery_QA.xlsx`\n\n### Stage 2 – Requirements Consolidation\nTransform discovery into structured requirements with:\n- ID\n- Process\n- Actor\n- Description\n- Trigger\n- Acceptance criteria\n\nIntegrations must not be assumed.\n\n[120 more lines in file. Use offset=130 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772753383672}}
